2) Core idea: two “strategies”
A) FormulationStrategy (maps decision vars → full XY)

penalty: decision vars are XY

reduced_space: decision vars are a subset, expanded to full XY using varList

sequence-pair / B* / slicing: decision vars are discrete structures, decoded to XY

B) SolverStrategy

penalty / reduced_space → your existing ens::DE

sequence-pair / bstar / slicing → SA loop (very small, fast, no allocations)

cpsat → OR-Tools CP-SAT (optional build flag)

